# Task 13: the Dockerfile now COPYs the app source into the image (so a
# `docker push`ed image is self-contained and runnable without the
# docker-compose bind mount local dev relies on) and runs its own
# `composer install --no-dev` at build time - so none of this needs to be
# (or should be) part of that COPY's build context.
